{{Youmay|the sabacc card|[[Legate|legislative rank]] or the [[Cipher Nine|agent with that codename]]}}
The '''Legate''' was a rank in the [[Centran sabacc/Legends|Centran sabacc]] deck. It had a value of 11, but trumped a normal 11 for tie-breaking purposes. When used in fortune-telling, it normally represented a being that was good at heart, with the suit providing more information.

